</h3>
<p>
  Share package since release 3.4, about Apr. 1997,
  communicated by <mixer person="Joachim Neubueser" data="name_city"/>.<br />
  Corresponding GAP&nbsp;4 package:
  <a href="/Packages/cryst.html">
